            +----------------------+
            |       FARMS          |
            +----------------------+
            | PK farm_id           |
            | farm_name            |
            | location             |
            | owner_name           |
            | created_at           |
            +----------+-----------+
                       |
             1         |      Many
                       |
        +--------------+----------------+
        |                               |
+-----------------------+       +----------------------+
|        CROPS          |       |       SENSORS        |
+-----------------------+       +----------------------+
| PK crop_id            |       | PK sensor_id         |
| FK farm_id            |       | FK farm_id           |
| crop_name             |       | sensor_type          |
| plant_date            |       | installed_at         |
| harvest_date          |       +----------+-----------+
+----------+------------+                    |
           |                                 |
           | 1                               | 1
           | Many                            | Many
           |                                 |
+----------+------------------+   +-----------+-----------------+
|  CROP_HEALTH_READINGS       |   |           ALERTS            |
+-----------------------------+   +-----------------------------+
| PK reading_id               |   | PK alert_id                 |
| FK crop_id                  |   | FK crop_id                  |
| FK sensor_id                |   | FK sensor_id                |
| reading_value               |   | alert_type                  |
| reading_date                |   | alert_message               |
+-----------------------------+   | alert_date                  |
                                  | status                      |
                                  +-----------------------------+


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| Relationship       | Type     | Meaning                            |
| ------------------ | -------- | ---------------------------------- |
| Farms → Crops      | 1 → Many | One farm grows multiple crops      |
| Farms → Sensors    | 1 → Many | One farm uses multiple sensors     |
| Crops → Readings   | 1 → Many | A crop has many health readings    |
| Sensors → Readings | 1 → Many | A sensor generates many readings   |
| Crops → Alerts     | 1 → Many | A crop can trigger multiple alerts |
| Sensors → Alerts   | 1 → Many | Alerts come from specific sensors  |
